		{"id":"3be7d5af2eee3b5d","type":"group","x":1140,"y":780,"width":437,"height":100,"color":"4","label":"Explanatory Structure (4 quadrants)"},
		{"id":"3786435b420d9680","type":"text","text":"Core question: what are the implications of AI for existential risk, for societies and economies over the next 5y -- and what should be done about it?","x":-152,"y":-37,"width":272,"height":157},
		{"id":"c74bc7df7c6f9b4e","type":"text","text":"☠️ Is there existential risk and how do we address that? ","x":282,"y":-200,"width":250,"height":72},
		{"id":"9b2e359134170e01","type":"text","text":"What is happening technologically with AI?","x":282,"y":-380,"width":250,"height":80},
		{"id":"a824a792b987bd00","type":"text","text":"How likely is it? Why","x":619,"y":-188,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"91f13a304bba7bd4","type":"text","text":"What do we do about it?","x":624,"y":-97,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"cb6170cc1305682c","type":"text","text":"We can control it  (not lights out ...)","x":275,"y":42,"width":250,"height":78},
		{"id":"6ea2f2ca6a4a8ca7","type":"text","text":"How does open up the solution space? (for a second renaissance)","x":613,"y":120,"width":250,"height":113},
		{"id":"48b531b55b2dc34c","type":"text","text":"But it exacerbates polycrisis and metacrisis ..?","x":613,"y":12,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"517778dee74734f5","type":"text","text":"Why is there existential risk?","x":613,"y":-280,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"21e7e266b8dcf43b","type":"text","text":"What new governance forms are supported / enabled by AI?","x":1406,"y":-168,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"33c4cf18948c3a7b","type":"text","text":"🏛️ Governance","x":1056,"y":-138,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"bac217f9f32b457a","type":"text","text":"How does AI support authoritarianism and endanger democracy (and vice versa)?","x":1406,"y":-92,"width":246,"height":89},
		{"id":"b32e6bbad794513c","type":"text","text":"Sensemaking and public sphere (cf polarization)","x":1060,"y":300,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"0af93152c6c0615a","type":"text","text":"Will AI take all jobs? How fast?","x":1406,"y":79,"width":250,"height":60},
